MARY PRATT: MEMORIAL BENCH INSCRIPTION IDEAS

For the church garden bench. Committee contact: Frank Palmer
Deadline: April 1, 2027

IDEAS:
1. "In loving memory of Mary Pratt, who planted beauty wherever she went. 1955-2022"
2. "Rest here among the flowers, dear Mary. Teacher, gardener, friend. 1955-2022"
3. "Mary E. Pratt: Her garden grows eternal. 1955-2022"

Notes: Mary loved the garden, taught elementary school 30 years, everyone in town knew her. Keep it simple and warm.
